{"tid":2099429,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方膝跪壓頸制服示威者　李家超︰無計劃禁止鎖頸式武力","createTime":"2020-07-08T08:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T08:37:13.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"678888f977080b9df8aac41e5f08ed6979caa3e2","tid":2099429,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"當美國有做同樣既衰野時就話美國都係咁，<br />\n而家美國唔做呢d衰野就唔見你講美國唔係咁？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4820400/org/a2fe26ce54c5d13fed1be52919e20cf9.jpg/6cosL5vEMpn9WswmFntjbL1f2f0aeLvw_9lRYf_ZUWE?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4820400%2Forg%2Fa2fe26ce54c5d13fed1be52919e20cf9.jpg%2F6cosL5vEMpn9WswmFntjbL1f2f0aeLvw_9lRYf_ZUWE%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=232c7429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員朱凱廸提出口頭質詢，質疑警方以膝頭跪壓頸部方式制服示威者的做法。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超今日（8日）在立法會上表示，當局無計劃禁止警方使用鎖頸式武力，並指由去年6月反修例至今，無因警方的執法有人死亡，「無發生過死亡個案」，表明警方沒有計劃禁止警務人員使用「鎖頸式武力」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到所指的「鎖頸式」定義，警員用膝頭跪壓頸部方式，該動作危險，李家超指，反對形容是「殺人武力」，認為警方過去12月的表現「恰如其分」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/495310/%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%86%9D%E8%B7%AA%E5%A3%93%E9%A0%B8%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E7%84%A1%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E9%8E%96%E9%A0%B8%E5%BC%8F%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F495310%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2586%259D%25E8%25B7%25AA%25E5%25A3%2593%25E9%25A0%25B8%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%259C%258D%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E9%258